fr.ecp.Group52_Project_IS1220_part1_AVEROUS_TOPUZ.Model.Stats

Class StatisticCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.ecp.Group52_Project_IS1220_part1_AVEROUS_TOPUZ.Model.Stats.StatisticCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StatisticVisitor

    public class StatisticCompiler
extends java.lang.Object
implements StatisticVisitor
    The StatisticCompiler Object implements the StatisticVisitor interface. It implements a visit method for each visitable items in order to compute statistics for each type of item.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pierre Averous, Nicolas Topuz
    See Also:
    StatisticVisitor, Network, Station, User, ParkingSlot, NetworkStatisticsSortingMethods
